3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with learning representations of data that can be used for various AI tasks. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with image classification and metric learning, which are important topics in multimedia analysis. 
5. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is also a possible category as the paper deals with learning representations of data that can be used for similarity search, which is an important task in information retrieval.
